        <p>US 20190128998</p>
        <p>RADAR Systems by providing lower level of phase noise</p>
        <p>US 20190128998 RADAR Systems by providing lower level of phase noise: A target detection system and method for autonomous vehicles is provided. A system may improve performance of RADAR Systems by providing lower level of phase noise, enabling autonomous vehicles to distinguish between the target vehicles, walls, traffic signals, pedestrians, road barriers, etc. The system includes a frequency synthesizer, one or more filters and a feedback loop. The frequency synthesizer may utilize a dual loop design comprising one main PLL and one sampling PLL, where the main PLL might include a DDS or Fractional-N PLL plus a variable divider, to reduce phase-noise.</p>
